@@TJvTreeView2.Menu
Description:
This property is a pagecontrol you want to use as menu. Each page in the PageControl must have a corresponding name in the items of the TreeView. So, when a user clicks an item in the treeview, the page is automatically selected. (This is an easy way to do menus like Netscape, Winamp or others like that).

